1- build the containers write this command inside the project "sudo docker-compose build"
2- run the containers write this command in the same path "sudo docker-compose up -d"
3- to display the images installed in your machine run this command "sudo docker images"
4- to display the containers running write this command "sudo docker ps"
5- to get inside the container write this command "sudo docker exec -it <container id or container name> /bin/bash".
for only the webserver container write this command "sudo docker exec -it webserver /bin/sh"
6- to down the containers write this command "sudo docker-compose down"
6- to stop the containers write this command "sudo docker-compose stop"
7- to remove the images write this command "sudo docker rmi -f <image id>"